parameters.name: EffectiveOrNot
parameters.description:
Specifies whether the redemption coupon takes effect. Valid values:

*   true
*   false

Default value: false.

parameters.name: ExpiryTimeEnd
parameters.description: The end time when the redemption coupon expires. The value must be in the yyyy-MM-ddTHH:mm:ssZ format.

parameters.name: ExpiryTimeStart
parameters.description: The start time when the redemption coupon expires. The value must be in the yyyy-MM-ddTHH:mm:ssZ format.

parameters.name: PageNum
parameters.description: The number of the page to return.

parameters.name: PageSize
parameters.description: The number of entries to return on each page.
